Heavy Weather is the 4th song on [[Jarvis Cocker]]s debut solo album, [[Jarvis (album)|''Jarvis'']].

The following is a list of people contributing to the song.

* Jarvis Cocker - lead vocals, backing vocals, acoustic guitar, tremelo guitar, Hammond organ 
* [[Richard Hawley]] - electric 12-string guitar 
* [[Steve Mackey]] - bass 
* [[Ross Orton]] - drums 
* Alasdair Malloy - percussion, rainmaker 
* Richard B Humphries - storm recording
